msgstr "/etc/sysconfig/ifconfig.eth0"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:79
msgid ""
"Now that we have said that, let's move on to booting our shiny new LFS "
"installation for the first time! First exit from the chroot environment:"
msgstr ""
"Après cet intermède, démarrons notre toute nouvelle installation LFS pour la "
"première fois&nbsp;! Tout d'abord, quittez l'environnement chroot&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput>logout</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>logout</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:84
msgid "Unmount the LFS file system hierarchy:"
msgstr "Démontez la hiérarchie du système de fichiers LFS&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput>umount -Rv $LFS</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>umount -Rv $LFS</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:88
msgid "Now, reboot the system with:"
msgstr "Maintenant, redémarrez le système avec&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><screen>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:90
#, no-wrap
msgid "<userinput>shutdown -r now</userinput>"
msgstr "<userinput>shutdown -r now</userinput>"

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:92
msgid ""
"Assuming the GRUB boot loader was set up as outlined earlier, the menu is "
"set to boot <emphasis>LFS &version;</emphasis> automatically."
msgstr ""
"En supposant que le chargeur de démarrage GRUB a été initialisé comme "
"indiqué plus tôt, le menu est prêt pour démarrer automatiquement "
"<emphasis>LFS &version;</emphasis>."

#. type: Content of: <sect1><para>
#: lfs-en/chapter11/reboot.xml:95
msgid ""
"When the reboot is complete, the LFS system is ready for use and more "
"software may be added to suit your needs."
msgstr ""
"Quand le redémarrage est terminé, le système LFS est fonctionnel et "
"davantage de logiciels peuvent être installés pour satisfaire vos besoins."

